          "name": "Can I do effective local SEO for under $100/month?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. The most impactful local SEO activities — publishing GBP content and blog articles — can be fully automated for under $100/month with theStacc. Add BrightLocal ($39/mo) for rank tracking and citation audits, and you have a complete local SEO stack for $138/month. That replaces a $1,500–$3,000/month agency for most single-location businesses." }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Is theStacc under $100/month?",
