        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What local SEO tools can I get for $50/month or less?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "At $50/month or less: theStacc Local SEO ($49/mo) — 30 automated GBP posts. BrightLocal Track ($39/mo) — rank tracking, GBP audit, basic reporting. Local Falcon ($24.99/mo) — geo-grid Maps rank tracking. Moz Local ($20/mo) — listing sync across 90+ directories. Mangools ($29.90/mo annual) — local keyword research. These five tools combined cover GBP content, rank tracking, listing management, and keyword research for $163/month total." }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the best free local SEO tool?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Google Business Profile (native) is the best free local SEO tool — full profile control, review management, and post publishing at zero cost. The limitation is everything is manual. Google Search Console is also free and shows you which keywords are driving organic traffic to your site. Both are essential starting points before investing in paid tools." }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does publishing blog content actually help local SEO?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Blog content targeting local keywords builds topical authority that Google uses as a prominence signal for Maps rankings. A website publishing 30 articles per month about its industry, services, and local area consistently outperforms one that publishes monthly or less. theStacc automates this entirely at $99/month — the best content investment available under $100/month." }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the best local SEO stack for under $150/month?",
          "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The best local SEO stack under $150/month: theStacc Local SEO ($49/mo) for GBP posts + BrightLocal Track ($39/mo) for rank tracking and citation audits + Moz Local ($20/mo) for listing sync. Total: $108/month. This covers GBP content automation, rank tracking, citation auditing, and listing distribution across 90+ directories — all under $110/month." }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
};
---
<BaseLayout seo={seo}>

  <!-- HERO -->
