              <p>Every other tool on this list tracks, audits, or manages. theStacc Blog SEO at $99/month publishes 30 articles per month automatically. That's the most active ranking driver of any tool in this price category.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>theStacc Local SEO at $49/month has the best GBP content value</h4>
              <p>30 GBP posts per month at $49 = $1.63 per post. The next-closest option is Localo's templates at $39/month — but you still write every post from a template. theStacc writes and publishes for you.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>The $108/month stack covers everything a small local business needs</h4>
              <p>theStacc Local SEO ($49/mo) + BrightLocal Track ($39/mo) + Moz Local ($20/mo) = $108/month. GBP content automation, rank tracking, citation auditing, and listing distribution across 90+ directories. Replaces a $1,500+/month agency for most single-location businesses.</p>
