              <p>BrightLocal's geo-grid tracking at $39/month and Local Falcon's heatmaps at $24.99/month produce actionable ranking data that matches the core output of tools costing 3–5× more.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">05</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Under $100 doesn't mean low-impact — it means high-efficiency</h4>
              <p>The tools on this list were selected because they deliver real ranking impact, not because they're cheap. At $99/month, theStacc produces more content per month than most $2,000/month agencies.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
