        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>30 blog articles per month at $3.30 per article — the only content tool under $100</h4>
              <p>No other tool on this list creates content. Every alternative tracks, audits, or manages. Content creation is the highest-leverage local SEO activity — and theStacc is the only sub-$100 tool that does it automatically.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
