              <p>Titles, meta descriptions, header structure, internal linking, and schema — all optimized for every article. Not a content dump. A complete SEO package per publish.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Publishes directly to WordPress, Webflow, or Ghost — no uploading</h4>
              <p>Connect your CMS via OAuth or API. Articles appear on your site automatically on a consistent schedule. No draft folders to review, no manual uploads, no missed publishing days.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✗</span>
