          <p class="ba-sub">For local businesses and agencies that need rank tracking, citation audits, and review monitoring in one dashboard under $60/month.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">BrightLocal is the most widely used local SEO tracking platform for a reason: it puts more local SEO diagnostic data in one dashboard than any competitor at this price point. The geo-grid Maps tracker shows your exact position across a geographic grid at $39/month. Citation tracking across 80+ directories, GBP audit scoring, and review monitoring from Yelp and Facebook add up to a full local SEO health dashboard. The honest limitation: BrightLocal shows you what's wrong and where you rank. You still need other tools to fix the content side.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Geo-grid Maps rank tracking at $39/month — the best tracking value in the category</h4><p>Same geo-grid data as tools charging $99+/month. Block-by-block Maps ranking data that shows you exactly where your visibility falls off and where to focus.</p></div></li>
